put these libraries in lib/:

markdown2.py    # markdown2 
mongokit/       # wrapper for pymongo
t.o.rnado/      # t.o.rnado web server + framework
web/            # web.py framework. i use it form component.
beaker/         # beaker caching lib
scrappy/        # will be used for last-resort data migration

also, install mongodb (statically compiled ver available), pymongo (c-opt), 
and python-simplejson.

